rComments: She's a great prof who really cares about her students. Always takes the time to explain things if you don't understand. Talk with her, she's a really interesting person and is gives great honest advice if you ask her about graduate school. Research methods is dry as hell but she tries to make it as interesting and educative as she can.

Very good professor, down to earth and super friendly. She is willing to meet after class and clarify confusing material. Reasonable and fair marker, if you work hard you should be able to do well. Would recommend taking her class!
Great prof! She really cares about her students success. She's a very fair marker. If you put the work into it you'll do fine in her class!
